This is a simple map for weapon Achievement. 30 ct and 1 t spawn.

All weapons included in the package

This is my first map and I hope you enjoy it! Don't forget to look on [www.kipteam.tk](http://www.kipteam.tk "K!PTeam site") if you would like to join our clan.

How to play:
This is a 4 player map. There are 2 people inside the maze and 2 on top of the maze. The people on top are the captains and can give directions. A team wins when all enemy players are dead. This can be accomplished by reaching the end and pressing the button or by finding weapons and shooting the enemy. 

It is important that you use tactics! 

Example:
You can kill the enemy captain to gain an advantage.

RACE_SEWERS BY UNREAL So, I wanted to make a "new" map, one slighly diferent from all the other race maps out there, so I took some inspiration from games like TonyHawks using sewers as half-pipes to make awesome maneuvers, and this is the final result. Also, consider this map a bump on this mod, hopefully there will be more race maps soon to keep this mod alive. About the map, its a pretty little map, 2 laps with a nice view under some city with a nicely scaled 3DSkybox, it has a few bridges over it and some obstacles, to make it look more urban style.

Map is on our server, Tango Delta Clan: Public Server
(8.9.3.196:27015).

-=Overview=-
Made by: -=(TD)=- PurplGunner
THIS MAP IS RESTRICTED FROM ANY CHANGES OR EXTENSIONS IF YOU DO NOT ASK ME FIRST.

Contact me:
XFire: purplg
AIM: purplgunner
E-MAIL: purplgunner@hotmail.com
WEBSITE: www.tangodelta.org

Gameplay: This is a game of soccer. You try to make the ball into the other goal. If the ball goes past the goal, the ball is reset into the middle of the field. Also, there are teleporters that go to the side of the map with an unlimited sniper supply and you can snipe the opposing team. There are 2 secret ways of getting to the other teams room outside the map (I like to call Lobby) but I will not release the way how, you will just have to find someone who found out, or just find me playing.

Tips and Advice: Try slashing the ball to pass it or shoot it into the goal. The more of a sharper angle down, the higher the ball will go.

-=Notes=-
Note1: I am not on AIM much, but on XFire everytime I am at home.
Note2: This maybe my final release unless a glitch is uncovered.
Please take the time to contact me (preferably Email so you can attach pictures) and show me the glitches so I can fix them.

-=Version Hisory=-
May 6, 2006- TD_soccer-v1 released!
---
May 25, 2006- TD_soccer-v2 released!
   Bugs fixed:
   Counter-Terrorists scout spawn fixed.
   A couple of leaks were found and fixed.
   Fixed the bug where you can score a goal against the terrorist by hitting the side of the goal.

   Added/Changed:
   Change the teleporter so there's only one and it teleports you to the correct place according to your team.
   Added another room on top allowing you back into the game or go to either CT or T lobby.
   Added more lines to the soccer field.
   Removed the pipe in the middle of the field in which the ball would reset to.
   Added more room on the field so a goal cannot be made in one kick.
   Changed the direction of the push so when you're on the right side of it (according to the way you're looking at it) it pushes you forward.
   Changed the look of the scout spawn so it's a better working/looking spawner.

Bravesurf proudly presents the first map in the td_ categody: td_facethevil
This map is built on the concept of tower defence, most commonly known, I think, from Warcraft Frozen Throne.

The map is small in size and easy to get the hang of.
The main idea is for CT's to send as much zombies to the terrorists as possible, and the T's should try to kill the zombies before they reach the end of the map. Simple as that.
The map counts how many terrorists there are, and set the difficulty both in weapon and health accordingly.
1-3 terrorist(s) = m249
4-6 terrorists = m4a1
7-9 terrorists = elite
10-12 terrorists = glock
13-14 terrorists = deagle
"But, deagle is better than glock?" you say. Not in this game. The more bullets you can throw at the zombies the better. 
The less people the more teamplay is required. And face it, if there are 14 stressed terrorists there wont be much teamplay. lol

Max : 14terrorists & 2counter-terrorists.
Remember to add these commands:
mp_limitteams 0
mp_autoteambalance 0

Have fun, comment, and suggest improvements!

CREDS:
Fibbs - Awesome prefab timer I turned into a counter:) 

/Brave
